      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "STANDARD FORM NO. 64",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "Office Memorandum • UNITED STATES GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : DIRECTOR, FBI",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, EL PASO",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "SUBJECT: [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "FLYING OBJECTS IN AIR",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "DATE: July 22, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "67C",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "New Mexico on several occasions to report that she has received information",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "concerning flying objects passing through the air. Some of the reports that she",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "has received concern light objects seen at night which have allegedly been follow-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "ed by explosions. She advised that one of such objects was reported by [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "[REDACTED] who works near Canjilon, New Mexico. She claims that 67C",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "others were seen near Park View and Tierra Amarilla, New Mexico.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "[REDACTED] called attention to clippings from various newspapers 67C",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "concerning \"disc-like\" objects seen in New Mexico and other parts of the country.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "[REDACTED] claims to be a student of radio waves and ray forms, and",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "contends that the above mentioned objects may be missiles similar to those appear-67",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "ing over Sweden some time ago.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "[REDACTED] has discussed the above with officials of the Atomic",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "Energy Commission, and has written the Secretary of War and other government 67C",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "officials concerning her theories. [REDACTED]",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "[REDACTED] for the A.E.C., has advised that officials at Los Alamos consider",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "[REDACTED] unreliable and possibly not well balanced mentally. She has mentioned to",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "agents of this office that she was struck by lightning when a child.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "On July 15, [REDACTED] came to the Santa Fe resident agency and 67C",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "advised that she had written to WALTER WINCHELL, promising him a story in connection",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "with the \"flying discs.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "67C The foregoing information is being submitted to the Bureau, inasmuch as",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "[REDACTED] has written to several government officials and Mr. WINCHELL.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
